metadata.name: The Seer of Commands
metadata.description:
Title:

The Seer of Commands - The Stuff of Nightmares

Artist:

Mike Sherratt

Edition:

1/1

Description:

This is the first collection that Mike has started to feel his style of art coming to life. He updated opensea with two outstanding collections and now he presents.

Stuff of Nightmares...

Ten pieces were all brought to life from things that Mike created using AI tech and then manipulated with Photoshop.

We hope you enjoy the pieces and have time to visit Mike's diverse collections.

Collector will unlock an image once purchased.
